news.title: Adani Group offers to relocate employees after cement plants' closure
news.para: The statement stated that 85 employees of Darlaghat plant in Solan and 58 from Barmana plant in Bilaspur would be relocated to nearby sister plants of Adani group.

news.title: Kochi: Assets of Holy Faith H2O builders to be auctioned
news.para: Holy faith H20 was the first building razed on January 11, 2020. The auction will be held on January 20 next year to realize Rs 42 crore.

news.title: North Goa collector directs Canara Bank to sell off builder's assets
news.para: The collector has asked Canara Bank to recover Rs 4 crore as the money owed to the creditors along with an interest penalty of Rs 50 lakh.
